{"tid":563311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"從黑豹一套戲睇得出有部分連登仔品行有幾咁低劣","createTime":"2018-02-16T18:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T15:40:04.000Z","uid":92376,"like":115,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6272cc4aebc490f90722830231b1a3a0b45717a1","tid":563311,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"一味戇鳩鳩喺度力架力架nigga奇俠咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話套戲係咪精彩到唔抵屌我就覺得唔係，但問心果班人只係純粹睇人膚色唔順眼而唔係真心評套戲差喺邊，而只係喺度種族歧視，又話影衰marvel云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑又唔諗下自己都唔係咩高尚人種，黃皮豬咋我地，自己都未完全喺世界抬得起頭做人就走去學埋晒白人果啲至上主義，出到去我地喺白人眼中根本同黑人無乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家呢部分連登仔做既野真係人唔笑狗都<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個討論區既質素就係比呢種人拖低晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b7dc4f97b56947e2a4f8b1b787c9fe669ace7c","tid":563311,"uid":86090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043458315b5d4ba2c707f897410942892871b0e2","tid":563311,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9b7dc4f97b56947e2a4f8b1b787c9fe669ace7c","tid":563311,"uid":86090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11329053c5b7eaae69f553abd0ce7cf8b4b04ef0","tid":563311,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"是旦啦。過幾日就唔記得嫁啦"},{"pid":"f3291669cacd314d89ffeb2a47a777fa650413d4","tid":563311,"uid":9